    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts precisely, making it a dependable choice for any driver. While the interior is clean and free of major wear, the exterior shows some light signs of use, including a few minor rock chips on the front bumper and very light surface scratches consistent with careful driving. All electronics and climate control systems are fully functional, and the tires have plenty of tread remaining. This is a solid, honest car that is ready for its next owner without needing immediate repairs.",
