    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all project seekers and DIY enthusiasts! This car is ready for someone with a vision to give it a second life. While it currently requires significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a fantastic foundation for a restoration project or a reliable source for parts. It\u2019s an affordable entry point for anyone looking to roll up their sleeves and bring a classic back to the road!",
