      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in showroom condition. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, while the interior remains pristine, featuring supple, untouched leather and flawless trim. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, with all documentation meticulously organized. Mechanically, it operates with the precision of the day it left the factory\u2014silent, smooth, and powerful. For the discerning buyer who refuses to compromise on quality, this is the finest example available on the market today.",
      "price": 48500.0,
